{
  "stem": "14091.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And from that time on, I was hidden, again, in-- they made a space for us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And this was the night when my brothers came, and they were frightened that not too long I can be hidden in the hay.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "So in the night, they dug-- in one of the parts of the barn, they dug a pit.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And they put in there candles, and some food, and a blanket, and thought if the Germans will come to look for Jews-- because this was a regular occurrence.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "They would go to people because some people would tell that some Jews are hiding.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And they would come and find them and liquidate them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "So they thought that if we would even-- we will see-- Piotr would see that some-- somebody's approaching their farm, that we will both jump into this pit and put over our head-- it was a box of sand with-- so done that nobody could ever-- even if they would take their bayonets and pierce through.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "Because this is what they did.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "They used to come with bayonets and look in the-- in the haystacks with bayonets, to look if somebody's hiding there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we had this-- they felt it secure enough that we would-- if the time would come, that we would use it.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They left back to the partisans.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then once more, they came to visit us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it occurred to me, I was hidden by myself in that haystack in the daytime.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Lots of times, [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Tzila ?] would join me, but most of the time, I was alone.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was very hard, as before.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The mice had a ball.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean they-- They kept biting and they kept-- it was impossible.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
